@carbonenginejs/runtime-trinity

CarbonEngine and Fenris Creations (CCP Games) are named for interoperability
and provenance context. This package ports CarbonEngine class structure and
behavior from the local CarbonEngine C++ source tree and uses ccpwgl only as
optional reference material when it helps explain JavaScript behavior.

CarbonEngine / EVE Online names, formats, and class semantics remain the
property of their respective owners. This project is not affiliated with or
endorsed by CCP Games.

